      "date": "2023-10-16 14:43:50.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nThese functions are still declared in libcfs_cpu.h. Should they be in a LNet specific (new or existing) header?\n\nAlso, this code seems closely related to libcfs_cpu.c, which seems used more widely in Lustre modules. Are you thinking of moving that to LNet too?",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "6afafc07d6162e3cf6914acf31637430c3deeedc",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 125,
        "name": "James Simmons",
        "email": "jsimmons@infradead.org",
